title: Backlinks support awareness.
pid: bc7db3ba-712b-40cb-83e6-3398a45f02e6
body: |2-
  They let you see why or where, which can redirect you from the what or how
  question that brought you there.
  Among perhaps other such 'why or where',
  backlinks allow you to see, and consciously choose among, your motivations.
